   "link": null,
   "locked": false,
   "text": "Identity & Policy — the ONLY path to tools\nroles: MASTER / TRUSTED / STRANGER\ncaller ID = routing hint, never auth\nS3 out-of-band approval (expires 5 min)\nS4 emergency/premium blocklist\nS5 caps (warn 80%, stop 100%) · quiet hours\nconsent registry · S14 kill switch · $ budget",
   "fontSize": 13,
   "fontFamily": 1,
   "textAlign": "center",
   "verticalAlign": "middle",
   "containerId": "policy",
   "originalText": "Identity & Policy — the ONLY path to tools\nroles: MASTER / TRUSTED / STRANGER\ncaller ID = routing hint, never auth\nS3 out-of-band approval (expires 5 min)\nS4 emergency/premium blocklist\nS5 caps (warn 80%, stop 100%) · quiet hours\nconsent registry · S14 kill switch · $ budget",
   "lineHeight": 1.25,
   "baseline": 13
