  {
   "id": "panelB_t",
   "type": "text",
   "x": 690,
   "y": 1140,
   "width": 600,
   "height": 450,
   "angle": 0,
   "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
   "backgroundColor": "transparent",
   "fillStyle": "solid",
   "strokeWidth": 2,
   "strokeStyle": "solid",
   "roughness": 1,
   "opacity": 100,
   "groupIds": [],
   "frameId": null,
   "roundness": null,
   "seed": 1281810601,
   "version": 1,
   "versionNonce": 854316682,
   "isDeleted": false,
   "boundElements": [],
   "updated": 1749769200000,
   "link": null,
   "locked": false,
   "text": "FEATURES\n• identity-aware answering — role per caller, persona per role\n• outbound tasking with goal, success criteria and $ budget\n• AMD branching: human / voicemail-after-beep / IVR literal\n• escalating reminders: notify → wait → CALL YOU → retry ×4\n   until you verbally confirm (“I’m up”)\n• anti-spoofing: sensitive actions need Telegram approval —\n   no spoken PIN exists at all (spec §2.1 forbids it)\n• compliance rails, hard-coded: first-sentence AI disclosure ·\n   consent registry w/ provenance · quiet hours 21–09 · no\n   recording · emergency numbers unreachable\n• operations: DRY_RUN rehearsal · /halt kill switch · $ ledger\n   + daily budget · /calls review · watchdog · degraded modes ·\n   nightly off-box backups · 90 d transcript retention\n• eval harness: scripted counterpart calls, hard-check rubric\n• swappable adapters: Channel (Telegram) · Telephony (Twilio)\n   · Brain (Agent SDK) · Tools (+ MCP servers)\n• deploy: setup.sh → Caddy + systemd · runs on Pi 4/5 (arm64)\n• 128-test conformance suite + CI (ruff + pytest)",
   "fontSize": 13,
   "fontFamily": 3,
   "textAlign": "left",
   "verticalAlign": "middle",
   "containerId": "panelB",
   "originalText": "FEATURES\n• identity-aware answering — role per caller, persona per role\n• outbound tasking with goal, success criteria and $ budget\n• AMD branching: human / voicemail-after-beep / IVR literal\n• escalating reminders: notify → wait → CALL YOU → retry ×4\n   until you verbally confirm (“I’m up”)\n• anti-spoofing: sensitive actions need Telegram approval —\n   no spoken PIN exists at all (spec §2.1 forbids it)\n• compliance rails, hard-coded: first-sentence AI disclosure ·\n   consent registry w/ provenance · quiet hours 21–09 · no\n   recording · emergency numbers unreachable\n• operations: DRY_RUN rehearsal · /halt kill switch · $ ledger\n   + daily budget · /calls review · watchdog · degraded modes ·\n   nightly off-box backups · 90 d transcript retention\n• eval harness: scripted counterpart calls, hard-check rubric\n• swappable adapters: Channel (Telegram) · Telephony (Twilio)\n   · Brain (Agent SDK) · Tools (+ MCP servers)\n• deploy: setup.sh → Caddy + systemd · runs on Pi 4/5 (arm64)\n• 128-test conformance suite + CI (ruff + pytest)",
   "lineHeight": 1.25,
   "baseline": 13
  },
