   "text": "SECURITY INVARIANTS (spec §9)\nS1   stranger reaches take_message only — ever\nS2   webhooks signature-checked · no off-switch\nS3   sensitive → out-of-band owner approval\nS4   911/112/premium numbers undialable\nS5   daily caps — warn 80%, stop 100%\nS6   AI disclosure injected, not removable\nS7   no audio · secrets never logged/stored\nS8   brain gets no shell/file-exec tools\nS9   relay WS requires single-use nonce\nS10  web_fetch egress filter (SSRF, metadata)\nS11  inbound concurrency/cooldown/minute caps\nS12  idempotent webhook handling\nS13  outbound idempotency keys (one pizza!)\nS14  break-glass /halt — owner channel only\nS15  transcript retention purge\n\nTHREATS: prompt injection · caller-ID spoofing ·\nforged webhooks · WS hijack · SSRF · toll fraud ·\nfinancial DoS · duplicate execution · PII honeypot\n· runaway agent → docs/security.md",
